{"tid":188792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有乜問題呀！？】清潔大廈都係慶回歸活動？ 張華峰質疑政府「篤數」","createTime":"2017-04-06T03:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T07:58:12.000Z","uid":73262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"711ffa8898c8ac6663127c38d2f59bda1749c6a1","tid":188792,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:08:37.000Z","msg":"民政事務局早前回覆議員的書面質詢，顯示政府於2017/18年度已預留6.4億元供舉辦或贊助多項慶祝回歸20周年活動，當中包括政策局或部門的撥款，最多為康樂及文化事務署，涉及1.94億元，商經局亦涉及1.65億元，各政策局和部門在港將舉辦超過300項慶祝活動。<br />\n<br />\n周四立法會舉行財委會特別會議，金融服務界議員張華峰質疑，民政事務局為回歸20周年活動預留7千6百萬元，但部份活動與回歸無關<span style=\"color: red;\">，如沙田區清潔三無大廈活動、國際氣候跨課程專題比賽、持續性的長者服務等，</span>他指覺得政府「篤數」，希望政府不要為自我感覺良好，便將與回歸無關的活動，列為回歸慶祝活動。<br />\n民政事務局指慶祝回歸不限於大型文化活動，重點是關愛，讓市民參與，「接地氣」的活動，都會支持，故鼓勵地區舉辦持續性的活動，亦為區議會提供資助，如可在活動中派禮品，令地區亦感受到回歸周年的慶祝氣氛。<br />\n仆街  清潔大廈慶回歸有乜問題呀<br />\n張華鋒瞓你個覺喇 阻撚住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d1e033056f3bf406909360a865793bda8dd1a6","tid":188792,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:28:10.000Z","msg":"Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600cad86f8bbd8d1b54afcaad7e5ed37f4150469","tid":188792,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56527569&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56527569%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170406&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=e75c4c8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56527569%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170406&h=14f7431b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56527569&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170406</a>"},{"pid":"dc8f0369c771a0e5af1168f949530ba9b54782c2","tid":188792,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"連回覆用語都「強國化」：關愛、接地氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108bc3a4e1d2be3b851a3ab0ad3207d70385e8db","tid":188792,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"為左呃funding可以去到幾盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2447b64ca866c076ddbc485f8eeece8cb96f456","tid":188792,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"記得當年有個耶撚佈道會都掛個慶回歸牌頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1139b40e7f88737684fdfd8971a9fc1bf193a7","tid":188792,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"乜撚野接地氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n接地底啲煤氣呀？"},{"pid":"5150158c7926a40628624f2b3c32a6e5805624d7","tid":188792,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"應該搞反隨地吐痰活動。某些年長人士好似理所當然咁"},{"pid":"7249a547ac30857831bc4bc1c489ec173fe7cb9b","tid":188792,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該搞反隨地吐痰活動。某些年長人士好似理所當然咁</blockquote><br />\n應該整個慶回歸20周年巴士不剪指甲運動"},{"pid":"b59e72828305156a5015da6c466e6622d1cd8de8","tid":188792,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"幾好, 起碼有D實際作用."},{"pid":"cea389eff557995876957b07ab27cbb20f1fd326","tid":188792,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:58:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}